Here are some custom, high performance aircraft I've created.

[Aegis-FE3](https://www.dropbox.com/s/t76mfbqg76j3h0m/Aegis-FE3.craft?dl=0) is a fighter/interceptor type craft, with an average range, good maneuverability, and sleek style

> [Javascript is disabled. View full album](//imgur.com/a/NEdpS)

[Proteus-HE1](https://www.dropbox.com/s/e3cz03u4kwu84h3/Proteus-HE1.craft?dl=0) is an incredibly fast aircraft with the capability to outrun most aircraft. It has the potential to reach speeds of up to 1,172 m/s at an altitude of 500m-1km

> [Javascript is disabled. View full album](//imgur.com/a/vZE3v)
